{"article_id":"PagaXFOGOugPimZP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Special counsel Robert Mueller said","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"one reason","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"he didn ' t recommend bringing charges against President Trump","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"is that it could have foreclosed Congress ' ability","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to impeach him .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"In his 448-page report","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"released Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Mueller concluded","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that Mr. Trump did not conspire with Russia","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to try to subvert the 2016 election -","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"but the special counsel said","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"the steps","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"the president took","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"to try to undermine the subsequent investigation into that baseless claim","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"could seem fishy ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"depending on one ' s perspective .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Those moves ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"including dangling pardons and trying to fire Mr. Mueller ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"never came to fruition","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"but Mr. Mueller says","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that was more because of the stoic efforts of the president ' s aides","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"to thwart him than restraint on Mr. Trump ' s part .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"\" The president ' s efforts","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"to influence the investigation","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"were mostly unsuccessful ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"but that is largely because the persons","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"who surrounded the president","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"declined to carry out orders","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"or accede to his requests , \"","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"Mr. Mueller concluded .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Mr. Mueller did not recommend prosecuting Mr. Trump","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"and offered a number of explanations for that .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"One reason is that the Justice Department ' s Office of Legal Counsel has a long-standing policy","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"against charging a sitting president , even in a sealed indictment .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"But Mr. Mueller also said","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"he didn ' t want to prevent Congress from being able to impeach the president","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"should lawmakers pursue that option .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"\" Apart from OLC ' s constitutional view , we recognized","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that a federal criminal accusation against a sitting president would place burdens on the president ' s capacity","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"to govern","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"and potentially preempt constitutional processes","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"for addressing presidential misconduct , \"","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Mueller said .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"While Mr. Mueller didn ' t make a final recommendation on obstruction charges ,","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Attorney General William P. Barr ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"who has spent weeks reviewing the findings ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"did make a determination .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"there wasn ' t enough clear evidence of Mr. Trump ' s intent .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Besides ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Mr. Barr said ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"it would be difficult to prove obstruction of an investigation into something","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that didn ' t occur","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"- in this case , conspiracy with Russia -","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"and that the president knew","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"to be fake .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"\" As he said from the beginning ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"there was , in fact , no collusion .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"as the special counsel ' s report acknowledges ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"there is substantial evidence","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"to show","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"that the president was frustrated and angered by a sincere belief","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"that the investigation was undermining his presidency ,","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"propelled by his political opponents","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"and fueled by illegal leaks , \"","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"Mr. Barr said .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Even given all that ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"the president ' s team fully cooperated with Mr. Mueller ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"and none of Mr. Trump ' s moves denied the investigation documents or access","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"it sought ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"Mr. Barr said .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Mr. Mueller appears to have disagreed ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"spending page after page","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"detailing what he said","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"looked like suspect conduct .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"\" If we had confidence after a thorough investigation of the facts","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that the president clearly did not commit obstruction of justice ,","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"we would so state .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Based on the facts and the applicable legal standards ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"we are unable to reach that judgment , \"","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Mr. Mueller said .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"\" The evidence","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"we obtained about the president ' s actions and intent","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"presents difficult issues","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"that prevent us from conclusively determining","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"that no criminal conduct occurred .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"Accordingly ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"while this report does not conclude","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"that the president committed a crime ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"it also does not exonerate him . \"","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"\" Even in its incomplete form , the Mueller report outlines disturbing evidence","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"that President Trump engaged in obstruction of justice and other misconduct , \"","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"said Rep. Jerrold Nadler , the New York Democrat","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"who , as chairman of the House Judiciary Committee , would lead any impeachment push .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"\" It ' s too early to talk about that .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"We will have to go follow the evidence where it leads , \"","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"though he added","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"that his reading of the structure of Mr. Mueller ' s report suggests","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"he was indeed trying to give Congress a \" road map \" to that goal .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Pressure for impeachment was already growing among the rank and file Thursday","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"- including a key voice in Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez , a bellwether freshman liberal .","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"She said","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"she ' d been reluctant to go down that path ,","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"but Mr. Mueller ' s report was a clear invitation .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"She said","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"she would be signing onto articles of impeachment .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"\" Many know","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"I take no pleasure in discussions of impeachment , \"","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"\" But the report squarely puts this on our doorstep . \"","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"A similar report by the special prosecutor in the 1970s provided a blueprint for House impeachment proceedings against then-President Richard M. Nixon .","depth":4},{"id":114,"text":"Nixon resigned","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"before the House actually voted on impeachment .","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"The crux of a case against Mr. Trump would be nearly a dozen different episodes","depth":3},{"id":117,"text":"where Mr. Mueller said","depth":4},{"id":118,"text":"the president ' s actions could be seen as an attempt","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"to thwart a valid probe .","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"One was Mr. Trump ' s attempts","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"to shape FBI Director James B. Comey ' s initial inquiries into Russian actions","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"and then firing Mr. Comey","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"when the director appeared to counteract the president .","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"Mr. Mueller found Mr. Comey ' s version of events more convincing than that of the president ' s team .","depth":4},{"id":125,"text":"Mr. Mueller also questioned the president ' s orders to former top White House attorney Don McGahn","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"to fire Mr. Mueller ,","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"which Mr. McGahn refused to do ;","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"the president ' s attempt","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"to hide details about a June 2016 Trump Tower meeting between his family members and a Russian-backed operative ;","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"and the public dangling of pardons for those","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"who might refuse to cooperate with investigators .","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"Mr. Mueller said","depth":5},{"id":133,"text":"he found it important to view the president ' s actions collectively","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"to determine","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"whether his motives were to undermine the investigation .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":271,"left":251,"right":270,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":251,"left":237,"right":250,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":179,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","